summary:
Getting older (and wiser), I’m choosing to do things I love. And I love selling brands, organisations and concepts behind the ideas I believe in.

I’m mad about out-of-the-box concepts, creative projects with the courage to challenge and surprise, rad designs and fine storytelling.

I have about 10 years of work experience, primarily in Marketing within B2B and B2C markets. I've worked for start-ups, scale ups and corporates in the Netherlands, South Africa, Slovenia and France. 
 
Feel welcome to connect, or message me directly.
